Daphne Pollard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daphne_Pollard 0 Daphne Pollard (19 October 1891 in Fitzroy, Melbourne – 22 February 1978 in Los Angeles) was an Australian-born vaudeville performer and dancer, active on stage and later in US films, mostly short comedies.
